    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-num mono">01</span>
      <span class="section-label mono">Why listen to me</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="display">Engineer. Business owner. But this one's personal.</h2>
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="lead">
        <p>By trade, I'm a part-owner of a civil engineering firm. We build what rural towns run on — water systems and roads. I've led our company's push into AI, building tools that do real work with real consequences. I use these tools every day. I know what they can do.</p>
        <p>But the reason this site exists is closer to home. I'm a father of three boys, and I've coached young men and led them in my church for more than two decades. I've seen what one good coach at the right moment does for a kid — and what happens when nobody shows up. I'd rather my sons — and yours — learn to build than quietly get consumed.</p>
      </div>
      <p class="pull">AI is that moment. Somebody needs to stand at the fork in the road and point toward the work. <span class="hl">That's what this is.</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

